public class HtmlTemplateExporter extends AbstractDataExporter
The class HtmlTemplateExporter provides a data exporter that generates and processes template files using freemarker.

    • export

      public void export(SampleContext context, File file, ReportGeneratorConfiguration configuration) throws ExportException
      从接口复制的说明: DataExporter
      Export data from the specified context using the given configuration.
      参数:
      context - the context (must not be null)
      file - the file which from samples come (must not be null)
      configuration - the configuration (must not be null)
      抛出:
      ExportException - the export exception
